{"TopicId":197592,"ForumId":46,"TopicTitle":"Forum UI Changes","CreatedByName":"Clamp-o-Tron","CreatedById":201818,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-20T20:53:21Z","PageNum":2,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"computercat04","CreatedById":207723,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-20T21:51:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223870345\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197592\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221603230644\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022205453\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Entropian\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, Entropian said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNope.\u00A0 Still there:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.dropbox.com/s/c39pb5yqg0rbfgz/Capture.PNG?dl=1\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Capture.PNG?dl=1\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-ratio=\u002237.33\u0022 height=\u0022162\u0022 width=\u0022434\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.dropbox.com/s/c39pb5yqg0rbfgz/Capture.PNG?dl=1\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt fixed for me.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Commodore_32","CreatedById":200414,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-20T21:51:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223870345\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197592\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221603230644\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022205453\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Entropian\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, Entropian said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNope.\u00A0 Still there:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.dropbox.com/s/c39pb5yqg0rbfgz/Capture.PNG?dl=1\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Capture.PNG?dl=1\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-ratio=\u002237.33\u0022 height=\u0022162\u0022 width=\u0022434\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.dropbox.com/s/c39pb5yqg0rbfgz/Capture.PNG?dl=1\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRestart your browser then\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DeadJohn","CreatedById":201293,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-20T21:54:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe new layout looks okay on my phone (Android), but poor on a large screen (Windows, 27\u0022 display, tested with Firefox and Chrome).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#000000;\u0022\u003EGray text on a 100% (or nearly 100%) white background is too bright and low contrast, especially when so many of us jump between KSP\u0027s dark screens and this forum. Please give us an option for a much darker background, with default text color adjusted accordingly.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"linuxgurugamer","CreatedById":129964,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-20T21:54:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWould be nice if we had options for the UI. \u00A0Most other forums I\u2019m on do.\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223870305\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197592\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221603228102\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002227914\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Vanamonde\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n49 minutes ago, Vanamonde said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThese things are usually not a big deal. No one even noticed the last couple of updates they ran. This one is having difficulties.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe ideal is to have no impact to the user. \u00A0The professional way is to do a planned upgrade.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is what I do in my day job.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-20T21:59:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMissed opportunity\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg data-ratio=\u002299.78\u0022 width=\u0022454\u0022 alt=\u0022ksp-meme-2.png?w=454\u0022 src=\u0022https://kerbalanders.files.wordpress.com/2020/10/ksp-meme-2.png?w=454\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KSK","CreatedById":61025,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-20T21:59:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI am clearly out of touch with modern website design.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe new Facebook UI is butt-ugly and now, so too is the KSP forum.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt looks like they took an expanse of white space and then sneezed UI elements over it. Are they actively trying to reduce the time people spend here?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBleh.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-10-20T22:02:05Z\u0022 title=\u002210/20/2020 10:02  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 20, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by KSK\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mr. Peabody","CreatedById":173591,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-20T22:00:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe text contrasts poorly with the white background on large screens, methinks.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"computercat04","CreatedById":207723,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-20T22:03:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223870356\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197592\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221603231144\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022196529\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The Doodling Astronaut\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 minutes ago, The Doodling Astronaut said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMissed opportunity\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://kerbalanders.files.wordpress.com/2020/10/ksp-meme-2.png?w=454\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022ksp-meme-2.png?w=454\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-ratio=\u002299.78\u0022 width=\u0022454\u0022 src=\u0022https://kerbalanders.files.wordpress.com/2020/10/ksp-meme-2.png?w=454\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nExactly what I am asking for lol\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DunaManiac","CreatedById":176003,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-20T22:04:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso notifications are green now.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Klapaucius","CreatedById":181256,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-20T22:31:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEDIT: This was merged from my own thread, so just to clarify: The original thread title was \u003Cstrong\u003E\u0022New Stats Panel on Right\u0022.\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003E*****\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThoughts?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have to say, I would like a way to turn this off. It takes up screen real-estate, and none of these stats are useful to me.\u00A0 The top poster is not necessarily the most thoughtful poster.\u00A0 \u00A0And if I click on the popular posts link, it does not take me to the full post, but to the profile page of the poster.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt seems like statistics for statistics sake.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSorry about this. I realize a lot of work has gone into this, and it is very easy to immediately\u00A0critique something. But this just makes the website look a lot less clean for no benefit.\u00A0 It does not need to go, but an ability to set a preference to hide the window would be great.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-10-21T00:06:20Z\u0022 title=\u002210/21/2020 12:06  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 21, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by Klapaucius\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ManeTI","CreatedById":167672,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-20T23:04:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHey \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/181256-klapaucius/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022181256\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/181256-klapaucius/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Klapaucius\u003C/a\u003E! They are gone.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"adsii1970","CreatedById":89014,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-20T23:05:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/181256-klapaucius/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022181256\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/181256-klapaucius/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Klapaucius\u003C/a\u003E, I do not see the statistics panel on any threads except the ones where I am the \u003Cabbr title=\u00221. Original Post(er). The first post in a thread, or the person who posted it. 2. Overpowered. A part or mechanic that upsets game balance by being too powerful.\u0022\u003EOP\u003C/abbr\u003E.\u00A0 I do not see that panel on other threads. Nor do I see it on this one. I\u0027m not sure why anyone would need to see those kinds of statistics unless they are just creating threads for the sake of getting \u0022likes\u0022 and want to know what kind of threads are the most efficient at causing them.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt also seems that the forum is a lot brighter - to the extent of being an eyesore. It seems washed out and faded. I\u0027m also not a fan of the round avatars we now have.\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223870385\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197594\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221603235073\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022167672\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022ManeTI\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, ManeTI said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHey! They are gone.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYay, I stand corrected! Thanks, \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/167672-maneti/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022167672\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/167672-maneti/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@ManeTI\u003C/a\u003E!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Geonovast","CreatedById":179753,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-20T23:08:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/181256-klapaucius/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022181256\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/181256-klapaucius/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Klapaucius\u003C/a\u003E, I\u0027ve merged your thread into the New UI thread in Kerbal Network\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RyanRising","CreatedById":79932,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-20T23:14:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGotta say, not a fan of the round profile pictures, or having humans as default. The people certainly loses a bit of personality, and I can\u0027t help but feel like the circles just waste space.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AlamoVampire","CreatedById":78020,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-20T23:17:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNot a fan of this. Imho its way bright and garish. I cast my vote for a visual revert.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n181710202020\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HebaruSan","CreatedById":156657,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-20T23:20:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223870327\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197592\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221603229597\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022207723\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022computercat04\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 hours ago, computercat04 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think there should be\u00A0also a dark mode.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223870356\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197592\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221603231144\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022196529\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The Doodling Astronaut\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 hours ago, The Doodling Astronaut said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMissed opportunity\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://kerbalanders.files.wordpress.com/2020/10/ksp-meme-2.png?w=454\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022ksp-meme-2.png?w=454\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-ratio=\u002299.78\u0022 width=\u0022454\u0022 src=\u0022https://kerbalanders.files.wordpress.com/2020/10/ksp-meme-2.png?w=454\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSince I installed \u003Ca href=\u0022https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/stylish-custom-themes-for/fjnbnpbmkenffdnngjfgmeleoegfcffe/related?hl=en\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ethe \u0022Stylish\u0022 extension\u003C/a\u003E today for other reasons, I made an attempt at a KSP forum dark theme config (also makes the user profile icons into rounded boxes instead of circles). It\u0027s not completely perfect yet, but I think it\u0027s good enough for me to keep using for a while:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://userstyles.org/styles/191139/dark-kerbal-space-program-forum\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://userstyles.org/styles/191139/dark-kerbal-space-program-forum\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022A7nHuPo.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002295.60\u0022 height=\u0022478\u0022 width=\u0022500\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/A7nHuPo.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-10-21T04:08:53Z\u0022 title=\u002210/21/2020 04:08  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 21, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by HebaruSan\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AlamoVampire","CreatedById":78020,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-20T23:29:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223870340\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197592\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221603230123\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022205453\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Entropian\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Entropian said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOk, I found a solution to the anonymous problem.\u00A0 There\u0027s a tab in account settings that switches it now.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere\u0027s an option at the bottom of the page to change the theme to something slightly less bright.\u00A0 Go to \u0022Theme\u0022 and change it to \u0022Default.\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEDIT: The KSP logo is still obscured.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhere is the theme thing? I cant find it and the new look of the forum is hurting my eyes its soo bright and frankly off-putting.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n182910202020\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Miguelsgamingch","CreatedById":201607,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-20T23:31:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWow.. The forum is sooooooooooooooooooooooooo\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDifferent.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"swjr-swis","CreatedById":152460,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-20T23:32:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI would really appreciate knowing who exactly thought it was a good idea to make everything on a page blend together to the point of making it near impossible to discern where a field or UI element ends and the next one starts. Basically, the exact same atrocious error made the last couple of updates, but then another degree worse.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ll do the same I did last few times: I\u0027ll give it a week or two before I revisit, and hopefully by then someone has come up with a half-decent complete style replacement so it becomes somewhat functional again. Otherwise, I guess I\u0027m done with this forum.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou know you\u0027re doing a good job reworking your website when the first thing half the visitors do is go look for ways to revert/undo/work around the new appearance. Whoopdee doo.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"tater","CreatedById":119411,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-20T23:36:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe text is too small/light to read comfortably.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have no tab in settings for adjusting it at all.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-20T23:44:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 